<speak version="1.0"
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis"
  xmlns:mstts="https://www.w3.org/2001/mstts"
  xml:lang="hi-IN">
  <voice name="hi-IN-SwaraNeural">


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 1 : PLAIN TEXT — NO PROSODY (baseline test)        -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Yeh ek simple sentence hai, bina kisi prosody ke.
    Iska matlab hai ki TTS engine apne default tone mein bolega.
    Yaar, ghar pe sab theek hai? Aaj khaana kya bana?
    Main office se thaka hua aaya hoon, aur neend aa rahi hai.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 2 : DATES — multiple formats                       -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ab hum dates test karenge.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Aaj ki date hai
    <say-as interpret-as="date" format="dmy">11-03-2026</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Independence day aata hai
    <say-as interpret-as="date" format="dm">15-08</say-as> ko.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Mera birthday hai
    <say-as interpret-as="date" format="mdy">07/04/1995</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Yeh event tha
    <say-as interpret-as="date" format="ymd">2024-12-25</say-as> ko.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Aur ek simple year:
    <say-as interpret-as="date" format="y">2026</say-as>.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 3 : NUMBERS, DIGITS, CURRENCY, SYMBOLS             -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ab numbers aur symbols test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Yeh ek cardinal number hai:
    <say-as interpret-as="cardinal">4523</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Phone number digit by digit:
    <say-as interpret-as="digits">9876543210</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    OTP hai:
    <say-as interpret-as="digits">482951</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Rupees mein price:
    <say-as interpret-as="currency">₹1,49,999</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Dollar mein:
    <say-as interpret-as="currency">$4999.99</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Percentage test:
    <say-as interpret-as="cardinal">87</say-as> percent students pass hue.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Hashtag aur at sign — yeh symbols hain: # aur @.
    Mere Instagram handle pe follow karo: @hinditech_yaar.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Toh total cost thi
    <say-as interpret-as="currency">$250</say-as>
    plus taxes.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 4 : ABBREVIATIONS AND CHARACTERS                   -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ab abbreviations test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Meri company ka naam hai
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">IBM</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Mera employee ID hai
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">EMP4872</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    WiFi password hai:
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">AB12XY</say-as>.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Yeh
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">HTML</say-as>
    aur
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">CSS</say-as>
    web development ke liye hote hain.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Normal bolne mein: HTML aur CSS. Ab character by character:
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">HTML</say-as>
    aur
    <say-as interpret-as="characters">CSS</say-as>.
    Fark sunaayi diya?

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 5 : TIME                                           -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Time test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Meeting hai
    <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hms12">3:30pm</say-as>
    pe.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Train chhoot jaayegi
    <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hms24">22:45:00</say-as>
    pe agar late rahe.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Office time hai
    <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hms12">9:00am</say-as>
    se
    <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hms12">6:00pm</say-as>
    tak.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 6 : EXTREME EMOTIONS — EXCITED / HAPPY            -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="x-high" volume="loud">
      Bhai bhai bhai! Sun tune yeh suna?!
      Lottery lag gayi humari!
      Ek crore rupaye! Ek CRORE!
      Main toh danga kar dunga aaj!
      Chal celebrate karte hain, abhi ke abhi!
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 7 : EXTREME SADNESS / GRIEF                       -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="x-slow" pitch="x-low" volume="soft">
      Yaar...
      <break time="600ms"/>
      woh chale gaye.
      <break time="800ms"/>
      Kuch samajh nahi aa raha mujhe.
      <break time="500ms"/>
      Itna khali khali lag raha hai.
      <break time="700ms"/>
      Kaash... woh abhi bhi yahaan hote.
    </prosody>

    <break time="900ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 8 : ANGER / FRUSTRATION                           -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="high" volume="x-loud">
      Maine tumhe kitni baar bola tha!
      <emphasis level="strong">Kitni</emphasis>
      baar!
      Yeh kaam kal tak ho jaana chahiye tha!
      Aur ab tum mujhe bol rahe ho ki nahi hua?!
      Yeh bilkul
      <emphasis level="strong">acceptable</emphasis>
      nahi hai!
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 9 : FEAR / NERVOUSNESS                            -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="high" volume="soft">
      Main... main nahi jaana chahta wahan.
      <break time="400ms"/>
      Kuch toh hai us ghar mein, main feel kar sakta hoon.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Woh awaaz... kahan se aa rahi hai?
      <break time="600ms"/>
      <emphasis level="strong">Koi hai wahan.</emphasis>
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 10 : SARCASM / DRY HUMOR (slow + flat)            -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="low" volume="medium">
      Haan bilkul.
      <break time="400ms"/>
      Bahut
      <emphasis level="moderate">shandar</emphasis>
      kaam kiya tumne.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Sirf teen ghante late aaye, deadline miss ki,
      aur file galat folder mein save ki.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Truly.
      <emphasis level="strong">Outstanding.</emphasis>
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 11 : WHISPERING / SECRET                          -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody volume="x-soft" rate="slow" pitch="low">
      Shhh.
      <break time="400ms"/>
      Yahan koi nahi hai na?
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Kal bade sahab resign kar rahe hain.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Kisi ko mat batana, samjhe?
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Bilkul kisi ko nahi.
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 12 : ROBOTIC / ANNOUNCEMENT STYLE                 -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="x-low" volume="loud">
      Attention please.
      <break time="500ms"/>
      Train number
      <say-as interpret-as="digits">12301</say-as>
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Howrah Rajdhani Express
      <break time="300ms"/>
      is arriving on platform number
      <say-as interpret-as="cardinal">4</say-as>.
      <break time="400ms"/>
      Passengers are requested to stand behind the yellow line.
      <break time="500ms"/>
      Dhanyavad.
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 13 : STORYTELLING — MIXED PROSODY                 -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">
      Ek baar ki baat hai.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="low">
      Ek chhota sa gaon tha, pahadon ke peechhe.
      Wahan ek budhiya rehti thi.
    </prosody>
    <break time="300ms"/>

    <prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">
      Roz subah woh uthti, nadiyan ke paas jaati.
    </prosody>
    <break time="300ms"/>

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="high">
      Ek din achanak... ek awaaz aayi!
    </prosody>
    <break time="500ms"/>

    <prosody rate="x-slow" pitch="x-low" volume="soft">
      "Budhiya... tera waqt aa gaya hai."
    </prosody>
    <break time="600ms"/>

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="high" volume="loud">
      Woh bhaagi! Jitna tej ho sakta tha!
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">
      Lekin phir usne muda ke dekha.
      <break time="400ms"/>
      Woh sirf ek bachcha tha.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Apna khoya hua pota.
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 14 : LANGUAGE SWITCHING — HINGLISH               -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ab
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">language switching</lang>
    test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Yaar mera
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">laptop</lang>
    ekdum
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">slow</lang>
    ho gaya hai.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Aaj
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">presentation</lang>
    ke liye
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">slides</lang>
    banana hai.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Meeting mein boss ne bola ki
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">performance improvement plan</lang>
    follow karo.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Toh ab main
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">seriously</lang>
    sochna chahta hoon ki kya
    <lang xml:lang="en-US">job switch</lang>
    karna chahiye.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 15 : EMPHASIS LEVELS COMPARISON                   -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ab emphasis levels ka comparison karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Reduced:
    <emphasis level="reduced">Yeh kaam aaj karna hai.</emphasis>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Normal: Yeh kaam aaj karna hai.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Moderate:
    <emphasis level="moderate">Yeh kaam aaj karna hai.</emphasis>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Strong:
    <emphasis level="strong">Yeh kaam aaj karna hai.</emphasis>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 16 : RATE EXTREMES                                -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Rate test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="x-slow">
      Yeh bahut dheere bol rahi hoon. Har shabd sunaai de raha hai?
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow">
      Ab thoda tez, lekin phir bhi dheera.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="medium">
      Yeh normal speed hai, jaise hum baat karte hain.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="fast">
      Ab tez bol rahi hoon, jaise rush mein ho koi.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="x-fast">
      Yeh sabse tez hai, bilkul auctioneer ki tarah, sun sakte ho kya mujhe?
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 17 : PITCH EXTREMES                               -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Pitch test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody pitch="x-low">
      Yeh sabse neechi awaaz hai. Bilkul deep.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody pitch="low">
      Thodi neechi awaaz, serious tone.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody pitch="medium">
      Yeh normal pitch hai.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody pitch="high">
      Aaawaz thodi oonchi ho gayi!
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody pitch="x-high">
      Yeh sabse oonchi pitch hai! Bilkul cartoon jaisi!
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 18 : VOLUME EXTREMES                              -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Volume test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody volume="x-soft">
      Yeh bahut dheeme bol rahi hoon, kaan lagao.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody volume="soft">
      Thodi dheemi awaaz.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody volume="medium">
      Normal volume.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody volume="loud">
      Ab zor se bol rahi hoon!
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody volume="x-loud">
      YEH SABSE LOUD HAI! SUNAAYI DE RAHA HAI NA?!
    </prosody>

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 19 : ORDINAL NUMBERS                              -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    Ordinal numbers test karte hain.
    <break time="400ms"/>

    Race mein
    <say-as interpret-as="ordinal">1</say-as>
    position par aaya.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Woh
    <say-as interpret-as="ordinal">3</say-as>
    floor pe rehte hain.
    <break time="300ms"/>

    Yeh meri
    <say-as interpret-as="ordinal">10</say-as>
    koshish hai.

    <break time="800ms"/>


    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!--  SECTION 20 : FINAL MIXED STRESS TEST — EVERYTHING COMBINED -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">
      Ab ek final test.
    </prosody>
    <break time="500ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="low">
      Yaar, main tumhe ek baat batata hoon.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="medium">
      Aaj date thi
      <say-as interpret-as="date" format="dmy">11-03-2026</say-as>.
      Aur time tha
      <say-as interpret-as="time" format="hms12">7:30pm</say-as>.
    </prosody>
    <break time="300ms"/>

    <prosody rate="fast" pitch="high" volume="loud">
      Aur usne kya kiya? Bill aaya
      <say-as interpret-as="currency">$220</say-as>!
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="x-low" volume="x-soft">
      Maine socha...
      <break time="500ms"/>
      yeh
      <emphasis level="strong">galat</emphasis>
      tha.
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="x-fast" pitch="high">
      Toh main seedha gaya manager ke paas aur bola ki yeh
      <lang xml:lang="en-US">unacceptable</lang>
      hai aur mujhe
      <say-as interpret-as="currency">$220</say-as>
      wapas chahiye!
    </prosody>
    <break time="500ms"/>

    <prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium" volume="soft">
      Aur jaante ho kya hua?
      <break time="600ms"/>
      Unhone
      <emphasis level="strong">maan liya.</emphasis>
    </prosody>
    <break time="400ms"/>

    <prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium" volume="medium">
      Yeh tha humara
      <say-as interpret-as="characters">TTS</say-as>
      test. Ummeed hai ki aapko yeh
      <lang xml:lang="en-US">audio</lang>
      pasand aayi.
      <break time="300ms"/>
      Dhanyavad!
    </prosody>

  </voice>
</speak>
